    <item>
      <title>经过数月的威胁，特朗普软化了阻止向古巴提供石油的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-threats-oil-cuba-sanctions.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫新闻秘书表示，在一艘满载原油的俄罗斯油轮抵达古巴后，美国将“根据具体情况”评估运往古巴的石油运输情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-threats-oil-cuba-sanctions.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 04:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>进攻与防守：在伊朗问题上，区别对英国领导人很重要</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/31/world/europe/iran-war-united-states-britain-starmer.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国在英国领土上扩大战机舰队，英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他正在努力捍卫英国的利益，同时让英国远离战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/31/world/europe/iran-war-united-states-britain-starmer.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯签署法案为特朗普重命名佛罗里达机场</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-airport-palm-beach-florida.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果获得美国联邦航空管理局的批准，西棕榈滩附近的机场将于 7 月 1 日更名为唐纳德·J·特朗普总统国际机场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/trump-airport-palm-beach-florida.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 02:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员寻求特朗普政府有关机场移民逮捕的答案</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/senators-trump-airport-immigration-arrests.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[机场安全官员一直在与移民代理分享乘客数据，但该计划几乎没有受到关注，直到视频拍摄到一名妇女和她的女儿在旧金山机场被拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/senators-trump-airport-immigration-arrests.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一枚美国新型导弹击中了伊朗的体育馆。这是我们所知道的。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/us-missile-strike-iran-sports-hall-school.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[精确打击导弹刚刚完成原型测试，就处于保密状态——包括陆军从哪些波斯湾国家发射导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/us-missile-strike-iran-sports-hall-school.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署行政命令后，运输安全管理局工作人员开始领取薪水</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/tsa-workers-paychecks-trump-executive-order.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统周五签署了一份备忘录，命令国土安全部向 T.S.A. 支付费用。官员们没有具体说明是否会定期向他们发放工资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/tsa-workers-paychecks-trump-executive-order.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 00:39:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥就其公民在 ICE 拘留期间死亡向美国施压</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/mexico-ice-detention-deaths.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 表示，墨西哥将采取法律措施，要求改善移民拘留设施的条件。她表示，自特朗普总统上任以来，那里已有 14 名墨西哥公民死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/mexico-ice-detention-deaths.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 00:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
